message: Hello Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs. This exceptional item is valued at $12000 to us, reflecting its high quality and unique features. Considering its worth and the benefits it offers, I am extending this opportunity to purchase it for $10000. I believe this price not only represents a fair deal but also allows for some flexibility in negotiations. Please let me know if this proposal aligns with your expectations or if you would like to discuss further.
